Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.39,0:00:39.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在嫦娥鎮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.95,0:00:43.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然住宅區域發展得很快
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.46,0:00:48.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在稍微遠一點的地方  大自然還保留得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.28,0:00:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天氣那麽好真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.92,0:01:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那都是因為我平日行善的緣故哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.88,0:01:04.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.83,0:01:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.08,0:01:09.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一會兒忘記做作業讓要同學借你看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.21,0:01:11.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一會兒第二節課休息就把便當吃掉…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.82,0:01:12.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.38,0:01:15.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  小博好過分
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.13,0:01:16.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底誰過分
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.32,0:01:19.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許的確如博士君所說的那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.28,0:01:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  小要到底是哪一邊的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.45,0:01:26.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麽要笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.67,0:01:28.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.59,0:01:31.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小博
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.89,0:01:32.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.83,0:01:34.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小  小鈴…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.82,0:01:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.78,0:01:46.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個香味  是八朔嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.03,0:01:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  喜歡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.84,0:01:49.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.51,0:03:43.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  到了哦  各位
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.99,0:03:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到達
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.46,0:03:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣好難受的  小鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.37,0:03:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烤肉天堂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.54,0:04:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鈴真精神
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.44,0:04:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小博真沒精神
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.58,0:04:06.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小鈴的興致太高了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.53,0:04:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.63,0:04:10.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別管那麽多
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.65,0:04:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很舒服吧  對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.71,0:04:22.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,餵  集合~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.62,0:04:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.29,0:04:30.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們自己來准備材料嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.06,0:04:33.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魚當然要新鮮的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.71,0:04:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.05,0:04:36.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麽  拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.61,0:04:40.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上鈎了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.96,0:04:43.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  好大一條
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.23,0:04:44.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大收獲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.01,0:04:47.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鈴好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.87,0:04:49.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.54,0:04:52.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也釣到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.44,0:04:53.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹得好  小要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.19,0:04:55.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.22,0:04:56.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害  好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.76,0:05:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,釣到了  釣到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.64,0:05:04.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  博士君呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.16,0:05:12.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魚都不去博士君那裏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.38,0:05:15.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都說了會分給他的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.41,0:05:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥真是的  好像較上勁了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.89,0:05:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,餵  小博
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.53,0:05:23.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別釣了  回來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.94,0:05:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.35,0:05:44.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久沒有見到那麽高興的麻奈了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.28,0:05:45.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.71,0:05:52.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來  這裏真是個好地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.37,0:05:52.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.15,0:05:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前說過的嫦娥狼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.57,0:06:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很久以前似乎也是生活在這一帶的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.02,0:06:03.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們所居住的城鎮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.11,0:06:06.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全被包圍在森林和自然中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.09,0:06:08.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.31,0:06:13.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我總覺得好像是被關起來了一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.92,0:06:17.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被這名為自然的巨大籠子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.07,0:06:21.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？那個…說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.51,0:06:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧  博士君
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.33,0:06:25.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一臉當真的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.36,0:06:27.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是因為要同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.53,0:06:30.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是詩歌  詩歌啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.27,0:06:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…聽起來不像是詩歌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.70,0:06:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  小鈴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.78,0:06:43.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到剛才還在這裏組裝烤肉架來著
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.66,0:06:47.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我稍微去找一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.59,0:07:10.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為…為什麽只有衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.15,0:07:12.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.76,0:07:14.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現變態  發現變態
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.80,0:07:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始擊退
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.52,0:07:18.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個裝扮怎麽回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.12,0:07:19.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可大意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.79,0:07:23.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭呀  小博不要這樣盯著看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.07,0:07:24.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來  為什麽是泳裝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.58,0:07:26.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是來烤肉的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.21,0:07:30.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士君  找到小鈴了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.43,0:07:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要同學你來說說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.29,0:07:34.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鈴居然穿泳裝…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.17,0:07:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  別這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.34,0:07:42.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別管那麽多  過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.08,0:07:43.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麽沒帶泳裝來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.97,0:07:45.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衣褲好不容易才幹的說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.21,0:07:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得那麽好的天氣  馬上就會幹的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.66,0:07:49.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別那麽亂來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.80,0:07:51.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快放手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.00,0:07:52.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.92,0:08:04.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小博生氣了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.44,0:08:05.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.47,0:08:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然生氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.84,0:08:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.72,0:08:11.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小博真的對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.24,0:08:14.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦  不用這樣道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.57,0:08:18.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  做了錯事就要好好道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.94,0:08:21.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以小博  就以此原諒我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.04,0:08:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.59,0:08:26.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.43,0:08:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嗎  原諒我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.04,0:08:29.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.56,0:08:31.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.61,0:08:33.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.27,0:08:47.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你相信小鈴的話了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.22,0:08:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的以為我會讓你看了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.14,0:08:52.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.40,0:08:55.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  不要戲弄我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.87,0:09:21.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麽了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.22,0:09:24.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  沒什麽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.94,0:09:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  八朔是拿來當點心？還是要烤？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.10,0:09:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烤？怎麽可能做那種遭天譴的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.71,0:09:45.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遭天譴…？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.45,0:09:51.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那在八朔上畫臉就不會遭天譴嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.80,0:09:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我專用的特別標志
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.44,0:09:57.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行  快蓋上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.07,0:10:02.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃得好飽  好難受
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.13,0:10:04.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都吃完了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.40,0:10:08.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一會兒去稱下體重  臉就會發青了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.78,0:10:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是真是美味
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.79,0:10:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最喜歡燒烤了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.40,0:10:13.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.05,0:10:15.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後再來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.77,0:10:16.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.67,0:10:22.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.84,0:10:24.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.04,0:10:28.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個我洗過後再送還
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.75,0:10:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別在意  就這樣好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.67,0:10:32.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.57,0:10:35.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣博士君的氣味就會留下了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.75,0:10:39.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  老哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.74,0:10:41.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又說奇怪的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.95,0:10:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑的  開玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.71,0:10:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩笑？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.64,0:10:48.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥的玩笑有時很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.39,0:10:51.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  老哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.70,0:10:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賭上小博的衣服和我決勝負吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.20,0:10:56.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鈴也夠奇怪了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.18,0:10:57.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擅自拿我賭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.90,0:11:05.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是累壞了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.51,0:11:09.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  今天真是謝謝你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.82,0:11:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用這樣道謝的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.37,0:11:16.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和博士君在一起我也很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.45,0:11:19.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才是要感謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.18,0:11:43.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有  小鈴釣到了那麽大的魚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.97,0:11:46.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而哥哥卻一條都沒釣到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.73,0:11:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天只是手感不好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.78,0:11:52.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人  連魚餌的蚯蚓都不敢拿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.36,0:11:54.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要讓小鈴來替你上餌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.00,0:11:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.24,0:12:15.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧  小博
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.83,0:12:19.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼻涕流個不停
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.43,0:12:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腦子也有點暈暈的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.04,0:12:22.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是發燒了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.32,0:12:23.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  都是我不好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.17,0:12:25.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天還算勉強撐過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.85,0:12:25.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麽辦  怎麽辦才好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.41,0:12:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來非得好好道個歉不可
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.34,0:12:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小博  作為賠禮…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.64,0:12:30.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.79,0:12:33.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可真無力吐槽了  現在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.49,0:12:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.57,0:12:35.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,病得不輕呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.02,0:12:38.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要去「中心」一趟？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.57,0:12:39.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「中心」？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.63,0:12:41.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是「嫦娥醫療中心」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.30,0:12:46.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一家綜合性醫院  我們都叫它「中心」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.68,0:12:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裏面最新設備一應俱全
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.82,0:12:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是家挺有規模的醫院
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.86,0:12:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  還是去看看醫生比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.27,0:12:57.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  我就跟你一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.07,0:12:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事  沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.22,0:13:00.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一個人也能去的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.71,0:13:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是小鈴你在醫院裏被傳染了感冒什麽的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.34,0:13:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不好辦了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.77,0:13:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  路上小心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.11,0:13:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.06,0:13:12.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鈴  你保護過頭了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.51,0:13:25.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的跟要同學說的一樣  好大呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.74,0:13:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外  來這兒的人也真不少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.94,0:13:40.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九澄先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.41,0:13:41.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九澄博士先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.47,0:13:43.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.42,0:13:58.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有勞您了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.06,0:14:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事  讓您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.69,0:14:02.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關系
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.36,0:14:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是九澄博士對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.44,0:14:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的事情  我已經從侄女那兒聽說了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.91,0:14:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侄女？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.92,0:14:12.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,栉名田…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.55,0:14:15.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眠她是我的侄女
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.04,0:14:20.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽眠說  班上新轉來了個奇怪的同學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.16,0:14:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「奇怪的同學」…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.02,0:14:24.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  沒什麽  沒什麽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.70,0:14:25.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.78,0:14:29.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在本人面前說他是「奇怪的同學」  的確有些失禮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.51,0:14:37.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感冒啊  要不要先驗個血？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.67,0:14:39.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驗血？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.32,0:14:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是為了以防萬一
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.90,0:14:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也給你開了些藥  回去的時候去藥店取吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.00,0:14:47.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  就開始抽血吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.35,0:14:53.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是要回去？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.32,0:14:55.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是方便的話  一起如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.65,0:15:05.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.29,0:15:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是院長栉名田
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.08,0:15:09.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下賢木
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.67,0:15:12.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得你們生物制藥公司的負責人…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.65,0:15:16.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是境井先生才對啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.86,0:15:20.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  不過從今以後  就都由在下來接洽了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.39,0:15:22.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這交接可真突然呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.16,0:15:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為一些公司內部的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.89,0:15:25.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給您添麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.62,0:15:26.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒的事  沒的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.22,0:15:31.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下手上的這份  姑且就算是敝社的産品介紹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.52,0:15:32.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「姑且」這話…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.85,0:15:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您好像有點缺乏職業作風呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.06,0:15:41.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣的  敝社預定今後要加大新藥的研發力度
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.31,0:15:43.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.68,0:15:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想  這或許能夠對院長您的研究有所助益
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.76,0:15:53.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.63,0:15:56.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,定不負厚望
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.83,0:15:58.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.57,0:16:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感冒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.61,0:16:07.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鈴她給你添麻煩了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.16,0:16:09.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒  哪裏哪裏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.68,0:16:11.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一誠前輩也感冒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.74,0:16:14.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我是來取一些常用的藥的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.47,0:16:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,常用的藥？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.77,0:16:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…  是不是哪裏有…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.21,0:16:19.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在擔心我的身體嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.69,0:16:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士君你可真會體貼人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.72,0:16:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的好高興
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.67,0:16:25.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來  博士君…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.85,0:16:29.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和小鈴她  已經吻過了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.39,0:16:29.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.12,0:16:31.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難不成  你…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.68,0:16:32.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.22,0:16:34.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「難不成」  是什麽意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.30,0:16:38.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如說  難不成  你對女孩子不感興趣之類的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.45,0:16:40.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那種事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.22,0:16:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可你看啊  雖說是我這個做哥的一面之詞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.21,0:16:46.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鈴她也確實挺漂亮的對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.17,0:16:47.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.49,0:16:51.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可盡管如此  盡管她對你是那樣的窮追不舍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.32,0:16:55.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你對她卻仍舊是坐懷不亂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.67,0:16:56.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.67,0:16:59.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是挺奇怪的麽？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.22,0:17:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.93,0:17:12.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？這路沒走錯吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.53,0:17:14.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一誠前輩…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.49,0:17:18.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是有什麽要緊事趕著回去辦呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.71,0:17:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不  也不是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.03,0:17:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是稍微兜了下風而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.30,0:17:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙你的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.03,0:17:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實  我是想能夠像這樣  與你單獨相處
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.53,0:17:35.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.34,0:17:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不好？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.36,0:17:40.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士君你的香味…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.10,0:17:41.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  哎…！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.74,0:17:43.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,取不下來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.27,0:17:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？  啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.36,0:17:47.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這算什麽啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.34,0:17:50.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住…  住手…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.14,0:17:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…  不要…  啊…  啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.47,0:17:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…  不行…  你…  住手啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.00,0:17:59.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.90,0:18:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.31,0:18:28.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.50,0:18:30.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？  啊…？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.32,0:18:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是開個玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.76,0:18:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.71,0:18:35.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.84,0:18:36.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.99,0:18:37.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綠燈了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.43,0:18:39.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.12,0:18:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.12,0:18:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鈴她也有說過  你很容易上當呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.89,0:18:59.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就饒了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.34,0:19:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  再見啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.15,0:19:37.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天  那孩子來了醫院一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.17,0:19:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「那孩子」是指…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.40,0:19:42.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九澄博士麽？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.83,0:19:43.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.99,0:19:47.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確  跟小眠你說的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.68,0:19:51.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偏偏又是在這個八朔收成不好的年景裏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.48,0:19:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了個那樣的孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.92,0:19:54.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.90,0:19:56.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道小眠你也不容易
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.97,0:19:58.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過還是拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.64,0:20:00.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.41,0:20:09.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,餵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.19,0:20:11.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是讓一誠大哥送你回來的對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.09,0:20:13.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥你也太偷奸耍滑了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.20,0:20:15.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.84,0:20:18.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要是也發了燒  去了醫院就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.68,0:20:19.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可真能說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.97,0:20:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都說什麽「去了反而身體會更不好」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.63,0:20:24.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？  有這事？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.49,0:20:27.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  朝三暮四
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.62,0:20:28.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.82,0:20:30.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不早點睡可對身體不好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.65,0:20:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我弄醒的好像就是你吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.19,0:21:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燒退了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.64,0:21:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  已經好了麽？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.87,0:21:15.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.41,0:21:18.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可別大意了  還是吃點藥比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.95,0:21:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.35,0:21:29.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.31,0:21:31.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.61,0:21:35.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燒好像退了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.36,0:21:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀  似乎還有那麽點呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.75,0:21:40.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經好了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.30,0:21:42.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一路順風
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.50,0:21:44.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  一誠大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.28,0:21:47.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.33,0:21:49.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一路順風
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.91,0:21:50.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士君
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.54,0:21:53.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…  我走了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.06,0:21:56.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  那  出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.46,0:23:46.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四匹狼  嫦娥鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.19,0:23:50.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,言傷悲  語無常
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.13,0:23:53.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其形異  人所無
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.46,0:23:58.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奉神靈  入社坊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.22,0:24:01.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那慘紅的月光之下
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.22,0:24:03.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少女揮下閃動著妖光的鐮刀
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.05,0:24:05.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這小鎮  白日裏處處祥和甯靜
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.12,0:24:08.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可入了夜  卻又似乎有著另一副模樣
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.72,0:24:10.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集  預感
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.10,0:02:14.19,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}愛之彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.23,0:02:20.73,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}接連著傷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.77,0:02:33.90,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}心口難開 「君莫泣」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.94,0:02:39.94,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}漸次斑駁  世界之歌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.00,0:02:46.03,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}身在旅途　至終焉之河
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.07,0:02:52.57,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}刹那之間  逢見君影
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.72,0:02:56.44,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}如日削月割
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.92,0:03:08.46,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}故鄉迢迢  時之彼岸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.50,0:03:11.52,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}與君共往
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.61,0:03:14.57,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}無愛無心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.61,0:03:26.26,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}夜之彼方  如幻蒼空
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:02.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.66,0:22:18.24,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}忘れないで　この思いは
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.28,0:22:28.94,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}僕らが信じた愛の歌
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.08,0:22:35.19,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}抱きしめた夜には
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.24,0:22:38.05,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}影が月でなく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.28,0:22:41.43,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}繰り返す罪には
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.47,0:22:49.99,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}戸惑いの月が満ちる　融ける
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.94,0:22:56.83,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}いくつものこころが　君を縛るなら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.19,0:23:07.44,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}堕ちて行く決意が許されるまで　愛なのと信じたり
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.17,0:23:14.77,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}かすかな声手繰り寄せて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.81,0:23:20.56,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}交わる闇の調べ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.68,0:23:27.33,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}繋いでいく　この思いは
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.37,0:23:38.02,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}僕らが夢見た時の歌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.10,0:02:14.19,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}愛しさはいつも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.23,0:02:20.73,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}悲しみへと続いてるの
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.77,0:02:33.90,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}君にもう一人きりで待たないでと　言い出せずに
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.94,0:02:39.94,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}色あせてく　世界の歌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.00,0:02:46.03,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}僕らは終りへ旅をする
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.07,0:02:52.57,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}その束の間に　君と出会った
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.72,0:02:56.44,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}命を削るように
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.92,0:03:08.46,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}時の向こうに確かにあった　遥かな故郷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.50,0:03:11.52,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}君とゆけるの
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.61,0:03:14.57,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}愛も見えない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.61,0:03:26.26,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}夜の向こうに　幻の空


